body:
Thank you LlamaIndex library creators. As a Data Scientist, I have found LlamaIndex to be an incredibly helpful framework for training LLMs on own data.

Recently, while going through the documentation, I came across custom prompts and noticed that the site had been moved from https://gpt-index.readthedocs.io/en/latest/how_to/custom_prompts.html to https://gpt-index.readthedocs.io/en/latest/how_to/customization/custom_prompts.html. I have made a minor edit to rectify it.

@jerryjliu Please let me know if I can improve it? Once again, thank you so much for all your hard work and for making the world of AI model development a better place.
